{"id": "3cadcdb1adb35f56499e09b2fe80142dd4617ffa00ad82abad33ba4931a65f59", "item_id": "0fc1542da9:0", "text": "Computes a thin-film interference effect on six spectral bands."}
{"id": "7cb650beadf6dfc4d28c676f5984ba6771ff0eadf7f91fc712258a9bf4126c97", "item_id": "0fc1542da9:3", "text": "The color that will be perturbed by the interference effect."}
{"id": "93334a97b82f3a742d6fe37ceeac84cbbe1df34d934174448fa185614d9d8195", "item_id": "0fc1542da9:4", "text": "Eta"}
{"id": "b52406e74afee798476d3f0485745bc4a93fdbebf1e94999d02e457b88dd1a83", "item_id": "0fc1542da9:5", "text": "The index of refraction of the thin film. We assume the exterior medium is air."}
{"id": "b11fb1f593a8c9b74868a5c23e2d9be49151b8b61520e0395e7939812d2bbf97", "item_id": "0fc1542da9:6", "text": "Spread"}
{"id": "9849731e96fbdef2dfbc62abe3a45d4a8b76f89db2d5cfd71cfc4b7bfc4e9c7d", "item_id": "0fc1542da9:7", "text": "The index of refraction's amount of variation across the color spectrum."}
{"id": "7b5944144275ea10a17c903d2d06c015e34740dab2ea4930aeb7573b43bb635e", "item_id": "0fc1542da9:8", "text": "Thickness"}
{"id": "4e7747ffd123b22a8895c092efe43491d5ba86d5c096047863cf23f95bb5376e", "item_id": "0fc1542da9:9", "text": "The thickness of the thin film in nanometers."}
{"id": "be2ce17a4ae3b3b78daca5a87735a440c76f47fc5848d5485056075740b727e6", "item_id": "0fc1542da9:10", "text": "Thickness Scale"}
{"id": "71fd23b986c0779567f2c48f0ec3822dffa938f0d801d1fb1177227b45888821", "item_id": "0fc1542da9:11", "text": "Connect a pattern here to modulate the thickness. This will multiply the"}
{"id": "260c0aac8b82cc8f36e209d455a70c1777ba85017947f2f0802707d827a8cd52", "item_id": "0fc1542da9:12", "text": "thickness"}
{"id": "0352209d4bcd7583f071429dd5aafd79f9c20f6494d918ae92895f1289f3d0e5", "item_id": "0fc1542da9:13", "text": "value."}
{"id": "c2d6d1452fc1d104a350b642f33f2c2afaceb6657978d4616429523ce64402b5", "item_id": "0fc1542da9:14", "text": "Front Only"}
{"id": "4d892fa56324086ba4ed2d40b6745e30f57c15ec5eb1c0c46599811d1fea4dca", "item_id": "0fc1542da9:15", "text": "Compute only interference on front-facing points. By default, both sides are computed."}
{"id": "11e1b24f86e144bbc59b2b9fb8d6d9d80b06582a73ac5173cfe1c6ae5522bf82", "item_id": "0fc1542da9:18", "text": "The color result."}
